      "span_text": "The non-adipose mass, hereafter termed fatfree mass (kg), was estimated as 9.1536 + (0.4273 × height 2 / resistance) + (0.1926 × weight) + (0.0667 × reactance) for male subjects, and as 7.7435 + (0.4542 × height 2 /resistance) + (0.119 × weight) + (0.0455 × reactance) for female subjects [CITATION_1] ."
